Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.83,0:00:05.24,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宇宙就是這樣\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The cosmos is all there is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:06.78,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}過去是這樣\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or ever was,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:08.31,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以後還是這樣\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or ever will be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:11.06,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟我來\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:14.50,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}30多年前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A generation ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:16.90,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天文學家卡爾·薩根站在這裏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the astronomer Carl Sagan stood here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:20.91,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI}1980年 卡爾·薩根在PBS拍攝了紀錄片《卡爾·薩根的宇宙》\n其紀錄片在超過60個國家播出 影響著全世界超過五億人口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:18.91,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}帶領全世界數億人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and launched hundreds of millions of us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:20.91,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}進行了一場歷險\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}on a great adventure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:24.74,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用科學去探索宇宙的奧秘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the exploration of the universe revealed by science.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.78,0:00:27.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是時候再次探險了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's time to get going again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.78,0:00:30.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這場即將開始的旅行會向我們展示\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're about to begin a journey that will take us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:33.85,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從最微小的到無窮大的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from the infinitesimal to the infinite,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.89,0:00:36.86,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從時間的開始到遙遠的未來\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from the dawn of time to the distant future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:41.19,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們會探索不同的世界和星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We'll explore galaxies and suns and worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:44.23,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在時間和空間的組合中暢遊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}surf the gravity waves of space-time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:47.60,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接觸生活在火中和冰中的生物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}encounter beings that live in fire and ice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:51.37,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}探索永恆不滅的星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}explore the planets of stars that never die,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:53.97,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瞭解和恒星一樣大的原子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}discover atoms as massive as suns
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:00:58.08,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有比原子還小的宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and universes smaller than atoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.11,0:01:01.25,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這也是關於人類的故事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Cosmos is also a story about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:10.12,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這也是先人們對星空研究的史詩長篇\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's the saga of how wandering bands of hunters and gatherers found their way to the stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:13.93,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}眾多英雄共同譜寫的史詩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one adventure with many heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:26.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們需要想像力來完成這次歷險\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To make this journey,we'll need imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:28.44,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但僅靠想像力是不夠的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But imagination alone is not enough
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:34.01,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為大自然的真實樣子是超乎想像的神奇\N{\fs14\fn微軟雅黑}because the reality of nature is far more wondrous than anything we can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:41.69,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}使這次的歷險因為幾代研究人員的努力成為可能\N{\fs14\fn微軟雅黑}This adventure is made possible by generations of searchers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:45.19,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他們嚴格地堅持一套簡單的規則\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}strictly adhering to a simple set of rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:49.03,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以試驗和觀察結果檢驗觀點\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}test ideas by experiment and observation,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:51.97,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以通過檢驗的觀點為基礎\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}build on those ideas that pass the test,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.20,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}摒棄未通過檢驗的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}reject the ones that fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:01:56.84,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用證據說話\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}follow the evidence wherever it leads
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:01:59.51,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}並對一切存疑\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and question everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:02.01,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接受這些規則\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Accept these terms,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:05.98,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是你的宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the cosmos is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:09.32,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟我來吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:47.82,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\fe134\fsp0\fad(500,500)\pos(190,278)\fn方正准圓簡體\bord0\fs20\c&H24efff&}宇宙大探索\n{\fs17\c&Hffffff&} 第一集
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:52.82,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:04:02.82,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在這艘想像之舟中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In this ship of the Imagination,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:08.90,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不受空間和時間的限制\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}free from the shackles of space and time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.97,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們可以去任何地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we can go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:14.24,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你想知道我們身處太空何處\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you want to see where we are in space,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:17.44,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要看向窗外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just look out the front window.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:25.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以時間來說 過去就在我們腳下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the dimension of time, the past lies beneath us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:31.53,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是地球2.5億年前的樣子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Here's what Earth looked like 250 million years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.70,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抬頭 就可以看到未來的樣子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you want to see the future, look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:43.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是2.5億年後可能的樣子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And this is how it could appear 250 million years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:45.81,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我們要嘗試\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If we're going to be venturing out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.68,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在極度廣闊的宇宙中聯繫\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}into the farthest reaches of the cosmos,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:51.61,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們需要知道自己的宇宙位址\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we need to know our cosmic address,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:55.35,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是我們地址的第一行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and this is the first line of that address.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:59.01,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:21.43,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們現在離開地球 這個我們僅有的家園\N{\fs14\fn微軟雅黑}We're leaving the Earth, the only home we've ever known,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:25.87,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}向更加寬廣的宇宙進發\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for the farthest reaches of the cosmos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:33.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們最近的鄰居 月球 沒有大氣層\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our nearest neighbor, the Moon, has no sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:36.55,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有海洋 沒有生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}no ocean, no life...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:39.95,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有天體撞擊的傷痕\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just the scars of cosmic impacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:55.94,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們的地球為我們提供了風和浪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our star powers the wind and the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:59.77,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為地球表面一切的生物提供能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and all the life on the surface of our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:02.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從水星開始\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Sun holds all the worlds of the solar system
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:06.95,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}整個太陽系都被太陽的引力場所包圍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in its gravitational embrace, starting with Mercury...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:29.40,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直到雲層覆蓋的金星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}...to cloud-covered Venus, where runaway greenhouse effect
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:33.04,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}失控的溫室效應把它變成一座煉獄\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}has turned it into a kind of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:40.78,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:45.79,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}表面積和地球相近\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a world with as much land as Earth itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:07:01.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一條岩石似的小行星帶\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A belt of rocky asteroids circles the Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:03.80,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在火星和木星的軌道間圍繞太陽運行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}between the orbits of Mars and Jupiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:19.62,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}木星被四個大衛星和幾十個小衛星環繞\N{\fs14\fn微軟雅黑}With its four giant moons and dozens of smaller ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:23.12,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}木星好像擁有自己的太陽系一般\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Jupiter is like its own little solar system.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:27.56,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它的品質超過所有其他行星的總和\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It has more mass than all the other planets combined.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:41.18,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}木星的大紅斑\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Jupiter's Great Red Spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:44.34,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它是一個比地球大3倍的古老風暴\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a hurricane three times the size of our whole planet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:48.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經存在了幾百年之久\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that's been raging for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:12.24,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}土星宛如太陽系中皇冠上的明珠\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The crown jewel of our solar system, Saturn,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:17.91,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被無數運行軌道和緩慢翻滾的雪球所環繞\N{\fs14\fn微軟雅黑}ringed by freeways of countless orbiting and slowly tumbling snowballs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:21.95,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每個雪球的體積相當於一個小月亮\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}every snowball, a little moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:56.45,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天王星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Uranus...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:58.45,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有海王星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and Neptune,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:02.79,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這顆古人未知的最偏遠的行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the outermost planets, unknown to the ancients
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:07.86,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直到望遠鏡發明後才被發現\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and only discovered after the invention of the telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:11.36,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在這最偏遠的行星之外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Beyond the outermost planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:16.07,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有成千上萬的冰凍世界\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there's a swarm of tens of thousands of frozen worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:36.22,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冥王星就是其中一個\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And Pluto is one them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:51.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我們所有的航天器中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Of all our spacecraft,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:54.64,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是離家最遠的一個\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}this is the one that's traveled farthest from home...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:57.88,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旅行者1號\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Voyager 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:57.88,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI}於1977年9月5日發射 截止到2012年6月仍然正常運作\n它是有史以來距離地球最遠的人造飛行器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:02.55,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她承載著我們發向未來的資訊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}She bears a message to a billion years from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:02.55,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI}歷經36年的旅行 離地球約187億公里 是第一個離開太陽系的人造飛行器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:05.32,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}關於我們是誰\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}something of who we were,
